name: Three Honors Malzahar
description: As the Order of Solace's leader, Malzahar wants to extend a gentle, guiding hand to all. It was only by following the tenets of the Three Honors that he was able to escape from a pit of cynicism, and while apathy may reign supreme, Malzahar will do whatever it takes to build a better world.

wikiSkinData.distribution: Reward for finishing the ranked season with Honor level 5.
